		<b:Row>
		
		<b:Column size="9" offset="0">
		
		    <b:Row>
			<b:Column size="8" offset="0">
			    	<b:Heading size="3" >Request Device Ownership</b:Heading>
				    <b:Paragraph>When a new device has been added to the VeliSphere Network, it will be visible for 60 seconds.</b:Paragraph> 
				    <b:Paragraph>During this time, you can lookup the new device by entering the device identifier in the search box below
				        and hitting the search button. The device identifier is a unique ID, such as a MAC address, and is provided by the device vendor.
				        Consult your device vendor for further information</b:Paragraph>
				    <b:Paragraph>Once you have found the device, you are able to claim ownership of the device and continue with its configruation.</b:Paragraph>
				    <b:Paragraph>If ownership is not claimed within the 60 seconds time window, the device will not be visible anymore.
				        You can restart the process by reconnecting/restarting your device. Consult you device vendor for details.</b:Paragraph>
				    
				    <b:Row>
						<b:Column size="3" offset="0">
				    		<b:TextBox ui:field="txtSearchID"></b:TextBox>
				  		</b:Column>		
				  		<b:Column size="2" offset="0">
				    		<b:Button ui:field="btnSearchID" type="PRIMARY" size="SMALL" addStyleNames="btn-block">Search</b:Button>
				  		</b:Column>
					</b:Row>
					<b:Heading size="3" >Found:</b:Heading>
					<b:Image ui:field="imgFound"></b:Image>
				    <g:Anchor ui:field="ancFound"></g:Anchor> 
				    
				
				</b:Column>
			
